{"tid":396164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係唔係做左兵？","createTime":"2017-09-11T12:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T12:52:22.000Z","uid":146180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3927a33956272e6ee88cdb79e7c0a6c806a2f7c","tid":396164,"uid":146180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"話説我有一個女仔friend                               我同佢差唔多每個星期都出兩三次街          大家仲會單對單出去飲酒                            有一次佢飲醉左 我送佢返屋企 送到佢去佢屋企門口既時候佢仲問我入唔入去坐下     仲同我講屋企冇人                                         但係當時我聖人mode上身 心諗唔可以乘人之危 之後就話唔啦我走先                       有次我send左一個friend張相 問佢收唔收留我個fd  佢答我：no 我只要你                 當我以為自己可能做到佢男朋友既時候    比我發現佢原來有一個拍緊拖既男朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   但係之後大家仲會單對單出街飲酒 做好多曖昧嘅行為                                                 我唔明我而家到底係點 我好迷茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5183bce56715a989a9d98b1e0b65c5dd5e298903","tid":396164,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"拍咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"67e03d7d03b58db19f5874e8dd9f196fa34e47cb","tid":396164,"uid":146180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍咗幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n半年"},{"pid":"0fe1f7670f1a7c0830f098095b87c310cc636bff","tid":396164,"uid":113005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:40:17.000Z","msg":"你係咪好鍾意佢？"},{"pid":"0b9f4b24c9451a0bc836f534da53530d6c1df111","tid":396164,"uid":14524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"原諒她"},{"pid":"861f979b4190efd97bdff06b66250769884cfd17","tid":396164,"uid":146180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪好鍾意佢？</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f1e2ddfb90298f621b9688c3c64a4ddb6598dc","tid":396164,"u